description: Life is chaos in a thousand ways, many seem peace, others are only unpleasant to the eye, others nobody knows, that is subjective, but undeniable, chaos was the first and will be what reigns, when have you seen something without chaos? As simple as that at the moment of writing this I am generating a constant chaos in my mind, the situations that are experienced at every moment are the result of chaos, thinking about chaos generates you to think beyond the superficial, generating chaos in your thinking opens your mind to something new, for better or for worse, it is subjective, it depends on the angle from which you look at it...
